  <title translate="true">GW Allocation</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">GW Allotment</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The GW_Allotment tab is on the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Farms_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Water Balance Subregions</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">It is used to specify </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Farm_Process" anchor="ALLOTGW" domain="ModflowGuide.hmxp" styleclass="Strong" translate="true">ALLOTGW</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, the maximum pumping limit for a particular farm&apos;s total allowable pumping. That is the sum of all the farm wells rates specified for a farm are reduced to equal ALLOTGW if they exceed it.</text></para>
  </body>
